1.2.3	If the old drive is set to master, set the new drive to slave.	St
1.2.4	Done.	St
1.2.5	You'll now need to have XP recognize the drive.	St
1.2.6	Go to Control Panel and click Administrative Tools, then click Computer Management.	St
1.2.7	On the left, click Disk Management.	St
1.2.8	Locate the new drive on the right.	St
